                self.board_squares[-1].create_square()  # Calls create_square method for last instance just created/added in the line before
                # Strap in, this is gonna take (probably way too) many lines of code.
                # Configuring the labels at the starting squares of each piece to have the image of the piece.
                # We also add to the dictionary the notation of every square and what it contains.
